{"name":"Ratatouille Pasta","slug":"ratatouille-pasta","description":"<p>Dinner hack alert: leftover ratatouille to the rescue! This recipe is all about transforming yesterday’s leftovers into a yummy, weeknight win. We know the struggle of trying to sneak those nutritious veggies into your kids’ meals. Who doesn’t love a pasta night, right?&nbsp;</p>","ingredients":[{"name":"bite-size pasta","quantity":"2 cups","additionalInstruction":"such as penne or rotini"},{"name":"Ratatouille","quantity":"4 cups prepared","additionalInstruction":"warmed"},{"name":"eggplant","quantity":"1","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"red bell pepper","quantity":"1","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"zucchini","quantity":"1","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"olive oil","quantity":"2 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Ratatouille Seasoning","quantity":"1 pkg","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"diced tomatoes","quantity":"1 can (14 oz/398 ml)","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"ricotta or cottage cheese","quantity":"1 cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"grated Parmesan cheese","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":null}],"totalTime":"10 min","servings":"4 servings","preparation":"<ol>\n  <li>In a large pot or&nbsp;<a data-item-id=\"bd092c36-a4ba-5b73-9abc-fa95c0102e9a\" href=\"\">Multipurpose Steamer</a>, cook pasta according to package directions. Drain and return to pot.</li>\n  <li>Add warm ratatouille and ricotta; stir. Spoon into bowls; top with Parmesan.</li>\n</ol>","tags":[{"slug":"steamers","name":"Steamers"},{"slug":"epic_life_lunch","name":"Lunch"},{"slug":"low_sodium","name":"Low-sodium"},{"slug":"one_dish","name":"One Dish"},{"slug":"valentine_s_day","name":"Valentine’s Day"},{"slug":"microwave","name":"Microwave"},{"slug":"dinner","name":"Dinner"},{"slug":"lunch","name":"Lunch"},{"slug":"vegetarian","name":"Vegetarian"},{"slug":"high_protein","name":"High Protein"},{"slug":"epic_life_dinner","name":"Dinner"},{"slug":"stovetop_978bc23","name":"Stovetop"}],"nutritionalInformation":{"servingSize":"","calories":470,"fat":19,"saturatedFat":8,"transFat":0.1,"cholesterol":40,"sodium":450,"carbohydrate":59,"fiber":8,"sugars":10,"protein":19},"tips":"<p>Make it a casserole! Transfer prepared pasta into a 9\" baking dish.&nbsp;Mix <sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> pkg&nbsp;<a data-item-id=\"d92e3031-1e62-4ac4-b311-a9cec5e5f320\" href=\"\">Crispy &amp; Crunchy Coating Mix</a>&nbsp;with an extra <sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> cup grated Parmesan cheese and sprinkle on top. Lightly brush or spray with oil. Bake in preheated 400° F oven until brown and bubbly, about 10 min.</p>"}